  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: #191813; -webkit-print-color-adjust: exact; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 11.9811px; line-height: 1.3em; font-family: BookSanity; vertical-align: baseline; padding: 0px 0px 0.8em; z-index: 15; break-inside: avoid;\">At 6th level, you can spend 6 hours in a lab, or similar environment, using drugs to enhance the capabilities of standard medi-gel. It takes 2 hours to craft a single enhancement, but you can apply that benefit to any number of medi-gel cartridges. To craft another enhancement takes an additional 6 hours. Instead of using time to limit this feature, your GM can choose to allow you to add X divided by 2 (rounded up) enhancements, where X is your Intelligence modifier; then, you must finish a long rest before you can create new enhancements. Only one enhancement can be added to a medi-gel cartridge.</p>\n<hr style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; color: #191813; -webkit-print-color-adjust: exact; visibility: hidden; margin: 0px; font-family: BookSanity; font-size: 11.9811px;\">\n<ul style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; margin-top: -0.5em; padding-left: 1em; color: #191813; -webkit-print-color-adjust: exact; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 11.9811px; line-height: 1.3em; font-family: BookSanity; vertical-align: baseline; list-style: outside none; text-indent: -1em;\">\n<ul style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; margin-top: -0.5em; padding-left: 1em; -webkit-print-color-adjust: exact; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 11.9811px; line-height: 1.3em; vertical-align: baseline; list-style: outside none; text-indent: -1em;\">\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; -webkit-print-color-adjust: exact; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; break-inside: avoid;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; -webkit-print-color-adjust: exact; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; letter-spacing: 0.03em;\"><em style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; -webkit-print-color-adjust: exact; border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Stimulant.</em></strong>&nbsp;After using this medi-gel, you have advantage on the next saving throw or attack roll you make within 1 minute.</li>\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; -webkit-print-color-adjust: exact; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; break-inside: avoid;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; -webkit-print-color-adjust: exact; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; letter-spacing: 0.03em;\"><em style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; -webkit-print-color-adjust: exact; border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Opioid.</em></strong>&nbsp;Within 1 minute of using this medi-gel, the next time you take damage that reduces you to 0 hit points but doesn't kill you outright, you are reduced to 1 hit point instead.</li>\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; -webkit-print-color-adjust: exact; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; break-inside: avoid;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; -webkit-print-color-adjust: exact; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; letter-spacing: 0.03em;\"><em style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; -webkit-print-color-adjust: exact; border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Steroid.</em></strong>&nbsp;After using this medi-gel, add +2 damage to all melee damage for 1 minute.</li>\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; -webkit-print-color-adjust: exact; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; break-inside: avoid;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; -webkit-print-color-adjust: exact; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; letter-spacing: 0.03em;\"><em style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; -webkit-print-color-adjust: exact; border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Minagen.</em></strong>&nbsp;After using this medi-gel, gain +2 damage to all biotic spells and cantrips for 1 minute.</li>\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; -webkit-print-color-adjust: exact; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; break-inside: avoid;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; -webkit-print-color-adjust: exact; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; letter-spacing: 0.03em;\"><em style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; -webkit-print-color-adjust: exact; border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Videlicet.</em></strong>&nbsp;After using this medi-gel, gain +2 bonus to all ranged tech attacks for 1 minute.</li>\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; -webkit-print-color-adjust: exact; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; break-inside: avoid;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; -webkit-print-color-adjust: exact; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; letter-spacing: 0.03em;\"><em style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; -webkit-print-color-adjust: exact; border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Styptic.</em></strong> Increase the potency of the medi-gel by 1 level (maximum level is Superior)</li>\n</ul>\n</ul>",
